	(27683, 0, 0, 'I\'ve lived here and kept this shrine with the blessing of the Alexstrasza for longer than I can remember. In its darkest hour, I\'ve failed... I fell at the feet of that damned deathknight... Bloodbane.', 0, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Text 1'),
