	(27156, 1, 0, 'Grim news, my pint-sized companion. Should we suffer a defeat here the ramifications will be felt across this frozen wasteland. Lord Fordragon and our armies at the Wrathgate will be defenseless against an assault from Naxxramas.', 0, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Text 2'),
	(27156, 2, 0, 'Yes, yes, I haven\'t forgotten Hyjal, or Silithus, or the march of the Legion, or every other damnable confrontation the 7th Legion has faced. It... I don\'t want the soldiers to hear this, Two-bit, but for the first time in my life...', 0, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Text 3'),
	(27156, 3, 0, 'You are right, of course, old friend. Let us hope that these heroes arrive soon.', 0, 0, 100, 1, 0, 0, 'Text 4'),
