	(29061, 36, 0, 'TINK $N. Tink back, mon! We be Darkspear, mon! Bruddas and sistas! Remember when we fought the Zalazane and done took he head and freed da Echo Isles? MON! TINK! You was a champion of da Darkspear trolls!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'special_surprise SAY_EXEC_THINK_10'),
