	(29227, 40, 0, 'My son, there will come a day when you will command the Ashbringer and, with it, mete justice across this land. I have no doubt that when that day finally comes, you will bring pride to our people and that Lordaeron will be a better place because of you. But, my son, that day is not today.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 14496, 'Highlord Alexandros Mograine'),
