	(349, 1, 0, 'Ah,fresh air,at last! I need a moment to reset.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'corporal keeshan SAY_CORPORAL_2'),
	(349, 2, 0, 'The Blackrock infestation is thick in these parts. I will do my best to keep the pace. Let\'s go!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'corporal keeshan SAY_CORPORAL_3'),
