	(23139, 3, 0, 'But... My lord, I do not understand. $N... He is the orc that has...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor OVERLORD_SAY_4'),
	(23139, 4, 0, 'It will be done, my lord.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor OVERLORD_SAY_5'),
	(23139, 5, 0, 'So you thought to make a fool of Mor\'ghor, eh? Before you are delivered to Lord Illidan, you will feel pain that you could not know to exist. I will take pleasure in exacting my own vengeance.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor OVERLORD_SAY_6'),
	(23139, 6, 0, 'Warriors of Dragonmaw, gather \'round! One among you has attained the rank of highlord! Bow your heads in reverence! Show your respect and allegiance to Highlord $N!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor OVERLORD_YELL_1'),
	(23139, 7, 0, 'All hail Lord Illidan!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor OVERLORD_YELL_2'),
	(22083, 0, 0, 'What is the meaning of this, Mor\'ghor?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_1'),
	(22083, 1, 0, 'SILENCE!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_2'),
	(22083, 2, 0, 'Blathering idiot. You incomprehensibly incompetent buffoon...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_3'),
	(22083, 3, 0, 'THIS is your hero?', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_4'),
	(22083, 4, 0, 'You have been deceived, imbecile.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_5'),
	(22083, 5, 0, 'This... whole... operation... HAS BEEN COMPROMISED!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_6'),
	(22083, 6, 0, 'I expect to see this insect\'s carcass in pieces in my lair within the hour. Fail and you will suffer a fate so much worse than death.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor LORD_ILLIDAN_SAY_7'),
	(23141, 0, 0, 'You will not harm the boy, Mor\'ghor! Quickly, $N, climb on my back!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'overlord morghor YARZILL_THE_MERC_SAY'),
	(21027, 0, 0, 'I sense the tortured spirits, $n. They are this way, come quickly!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_START'),
	(21027, 1, 0, 'Watch out!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_AGGRO1'),
	(21027, 1, 1, 'Naga attackers! Defend yourself!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_AGGRO2'),
	(21027, 2, 0, 'Grant me protection $n, I must break trough their foul magic!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_PROGRESS1'),
	(21027, 3, 0, 'The naga of Coilskar are exceptionally cruel to their prisoners. It is a miracle that I survived inside that watery prison for as long as I did. Earthmother be praised.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_PROGRESS2'),
	(21027, 3, 1, 'Lady Vashj must answer for these atrocities. She must be brought to justice!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_PROGRESS4'),
	(21027, 3, 2, 'The tumultuous nature of the great waterways of Azeroth and Draenor are a direct result of tormented water spirits.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_PROGRESS5'),
	(21027, 4, 0, 'Now we must find the exit.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_FIND_EXIT'),
	(21027, 5, 0, 'It shouldn\'t be much further, $n. The exit is just up ahead.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_JUST_AHEAD'),
	(21027, 6, 0, 'Thank you, $n. Please return to my brethren at the Altar of Damnation, near the Hand of Gul\'dan, and tell them that Wilda is safe. May the Earthmother watch over you...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'wilda SAY_WIL_END'),
	(19685, 0, 0, 'Follow me, stranger. This won\'t take long.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_0'),
	(19685, 1, 0, 'Shattrath was once the draenei capital of this world. Its name means "dwelling of light."', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_1'),
	(19685, 2, 0, 'When the Burning Legion turned the orcs against the draenei, the fiercest battle was fought here. The draenei fought tooth and nail, but in the end the city fell.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_2'),
	(19685, 3, 0, 'The city was left in ruins and darkness... until the Sha\'tar arrived.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_3'),
	(19685, 4, 0, 'Let us go into the Lower City. I will warn you that as one of the only safe havens in Outland, Shattrath has attracted droves of refugees from all wars, current and past.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_4'),
	(19685, 5, 0, 'The Sha\'tar, or "born from light" are the naaru that came to Outland to fight the demons of the Burning Legion.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_5'),
	(19685, 6, 0, 'They were drawn to the ruins of Shattrath City where a small remnant of the draenei priesthood conducted its rites inside a ruined temple on this very spot.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_6'),
	(19685, 7, 0, 'The priesthood, known as the Aldor, quickly regained its strength as word spread that the naaru had returned and reconstruction soon began. The ruined temple is now used as an infirmary for injured refugees.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_7'),
	(19685, 8, 0, 'It wouldn\'t be long, however, before the city came under attack once again. This time, the attack came from Illidan\'s armies. A large regiment of blood elves had been sent by Illidan\'s ally, Kael\'thas Sunstrider, to lay waste to the city.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_8'),
	(19685, 9, 0, 'As the regiment of blood elves crossed this very bridge, the Aldor\'s exarchs and vindicators lined up to defend the Terrace of Light. But then the unexpected happened.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_9'),
	(19685, 10, 0, 'The blood elves laid down their weapons in front of the city\'s defenders; their leader, a blood elf elder known as Voren\'thal, stormed into the Terrace of Light and demanded to speak to A\'dal.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_10'),
	(19685, 11, 0, 'As the naaru approached him, Voren\'thal kneeled before him and uttered the following words: "I\'ve seen you in a vision, naaru. My race\'s only hope for survival lies with you. My followers and I are here to serve you."', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_11'),
	(19685, 12, 0, 'The defection of Voren\'thal and his followers was the largest loss ever incurred by Kael\'s forces. And these weren\'t just any blood elves. Many of the best and brightest amongst Kael\'s scholars and magisters had been swayed by Voren\'thal\'s influence.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_12'),
	(19685, 13, 0, 'The naaru accepted the defectors, who would become known as the Scryers; their dwelling lies in the platform above. Only those initiated with the Scryers are allowed there.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_13'),
	(19685, 14, 0, 'The Aldor are followers of the Light and forgiveness and redemption are values they understand. However, they found hard to forget the deeds of the blood elves while under Kael\'s command.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_14'),
	(19685, 15, 0, 'Many of the priesthood had been slain by the same magisters who now vowed to serve the naaru. They were not happy to share the city with their former enemies.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_15'),
	(19685, 16, 0, 'The Aldor\'s most holy temple and its surrounding dwellings lie on the terrace above. As a holy site, only the initiated are welcome inside.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_16'),
	(19685, 17, 0, 'The attacks against Shattrath continued, but the city did not fall, as you can see. On the contrary, the naaru known as Xi\'ri led a successful incursion into Shadowmoon Valley - Illidan\'s doorstep.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_17'),
	(19685, 18, 0, 'There he continues to wage war on Illidan with the assistance of the Aldor and the Scryers. The two factions have not given up on their old feuds, though.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_18'),
	(19685, 19, 0, 'Such is their animosity that they vie for the honor of being sent to assist the naaru there. Each day, that decision is made here by A\'dal. The armies gather here to receive A\'dal\'s blessing before heading to Shadowmoon.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_19'),
	(19685, 20, 0, 'Khadgar should be ready to see you again. Just remember that to serve the Sha\'tar you will most likely have to ally with the Aldor or the Scryers. And seeking the favor of one group will cause the others\' dislike.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_20'),
	(19685, 21, 0, 'Good luck stranger, and welcome to Shattrath City.', 15, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'kservant SAY_KHAD_SERV_21'),
	(19720, 0, 0, 'Time to teach you a lesson in manners, little $Gboy:girl;!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'larry SAY_START'),
	(19720, 1, 0, 'Now I\'m gonna give you to the count of \'3\' to get out of here before I sick the dogs on you.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'larry SAY_COUNT'),
	(19720, 2, 0, '1...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'larry SAY_COUNT_1'),
	(19720, 3, 0, '2...', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'larry SAY_COUNT_2'),
	(19720, 4, 0, 'Time to meet your maker!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'larry SAY_ATTACK_5'),
	(19720, 5, 0, 'Alright, we give up! Don\'t hurt us!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'larry SAY_GIVEUP'),
	(20912, 0, 0, 'It is a small matter to control the mind of the weak... for I bear allegiance to powers untouched by time, unmoved by fate. No force on this world or beyond harbors the strength to bend our knee... not even the mighty Legion!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11122, 'skyriss SAY_INTRO'),
	(20912, 1, 0, 'Bear witness to the agent of your demise!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11123, 'skyriss SAY_AGGRO'),
	(20912, 2, 0, 'Your fate is written!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11124, 'skyriss SAY_KILL_1'),
	(20912, 2, 1, 'The chaos I have sown here is but a taste...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11125, 'skyriss SAY_KILL_2'),
	(20912, 3, 0, 'You will do my bidding, weakling.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11127, 'skyriss SAY_MIND_1'),
	(20912, 3, 1, 'Your will is no longer your own.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11128, 'skyriss SAY_MIND_2'),
	(20912, 4, 0, 'Flee in terror!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11129, 'skyriss SAY_FEAR_1'),
	(20912, 4, 1, 'I will show you horrors undreamed of!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11130, 'skyriss SAY_FEAR_2'),
	(20912, 5, 0, 'We span the universe, as countless as the stars!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11131, 'skyriss SAY_IMAGE'),
	(20912, 6, 0, 'I am merely one of... infinite multitudes.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11126, 'skyriss SAY_DEATH'),
	(17975, 0, 0, 'What are you doing? These specimens are very delicate!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11144, 'freywinn SAY_AGGRO'),
	(17975, 1, 0, 'Your life cycle is now concluded!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11145, 'freywinn SAY_KILL_1'),
	(17975, 1, 1, 'You will feed the worms.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11146, 'freywinn SAY_KILL_2'),
	(17975, 2, 0, 'Endorel aluminor!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11147, 'freywinn SAY_TREE_1'),
	(17975, 2, 1, 'Nature bends to my will!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11148, 'freywinn SAY_TREE_2'),
	(17975, 3, 0, 'The specimens...must be preserved.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11149, 'freywinn SAY_DEATH'),
	(17980, 0, 0, 'emits a strange noise.', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'laj EMOTE_SUMMON'),
	(17977, 0, 0, 'Who disturbs this sanctuary?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11230, 'warp SAY_AGGRO'),
	(17977, 1, 0, 'You must die! But wait: this does not-- No, no... you must die!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11231, 'warp SAY_SLAY_1'),
	(17977, 1, 1, 'What am I doing? Why do I...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11232, 'warp SAY_SLAY_2'),
	(17977, 2, 0, 'Children, come to me!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11233, 'warp SAY_SUMMON_1'),
	(17977, 2, 1, 'Maybe this is not-- No, we fight! Come to my aid.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11234, 'warp SAY_SUMMON_2'),
	(17977, 3, 0, 'So... confused. Do not... belong here!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11235, 'warp SAY_DEATH'),
	(18805, 0, 0, 'Tal anu\'men no Sin\'dorei!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11134, 'solarian SAY_AGGRO'),
	(18805, 1, 0, 'Ha ha ha! You are hopelessly outmatched!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11139, 'solarian SAY_SUMMON1'),
	(18805, 2, 0, 'I will crush your delusions of grandeur!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11140, 'solarian SAY_SUMMON2'),
	(18805, 3, 0, 'Your soul belongs to the Abyss!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11136, 'solarian SAY_KILL1'),
	(18805, 3, 1, 'By the blood of the Highborne!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11137, 'solarian SAY_KILL2'),
	(18805, 3, 2, 'For the Sunwell!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11138, 'solarian SAY_KILL3'),
	(18805, 4, 0, 'The warmth of the sun... awaits.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11135, 'solarian SAY_DEATH'),
	(18805, 5, 0, 'Enough of this! Now I call upon the fury of the cosmos itself.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'solarian SAY_VOIDA'),
	(18805, 6, 0, 'I become ONE... with the VOID!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'solarian SAY_VOIDB'),
	(19622, 0, 0, 'Energy. Power. My people are addicted to it... a dependence made manifest after the Sunwell was destroyed. Welcome... to the future. A pity you are too late to stop it. No one can stop me now! Selama ashal\'anore!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11256, 'kaelthas SAY_INTRO'),
	(19622, 1, 0, 'Capernian will see to it that your stay here is a short one.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11257, 'kaelthas SAY_INTRO_CAPERNIAN'),
	(19622, 2, 0, 'Well done, you have proven worthy to test your skills against my master engineer, Telonicus.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11258, 'kaelthas SAY_INTRO_TELONICUS'),
	(19622, 3, 0, 'Let us see how your nerves hold up against the Darkener, Thaladred.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11259, 'kaelthas SAY_INTRO_THALADRED'),
	(19622, 4, 0, 'You have persevered against some of my best advisors... but none can withstand the might of the Blood Hammer. Behold, Lord Sanguinar!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11260, 'kaelthas SAY_INTRO_SANGUINAR'),
	(19622, 5, 0, 'As you see, I have many weapons in my arsenal...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11261, 'kaelthas SAY_PHASE2_WEAPON'),
	(19622, 6, 0, 'Perhaps I underestimated you. It would be unfair to make you fight all four advisors at once, but... fair treatment was never shown to my people. I\'m just returning the favor.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11262, 'kaelthas SAY_PHASE3_ADVANCE'),
	(19622, 7, 0, 'Alas, sometimes one must take matters into one\'s own hands. Balamore shanal!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11263, 'kaelthas SAY_PHASE4_INTRO2'),
	(19622, 8, 0, 'I have not come this far to be stopped! The future I have planned will not be jeopardized! Now you will taste true power!!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11273, 'kaelthas SAY_PHASE5_NUTS'),
	(19622, 9, 0, 'You will not prevail.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11270, 'kaelthas SAY_SLAY1'),
	(19622, 9, 1, 'You gambled...and lost.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11271, 'kaelthas SAY_SLAY2'),
	(19622, 9, 2, 'This was Child\'s play.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11272, 'kaelthas SAY_SLAY3'),
	(19622, 10, 0, 'Obey me.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11268, 'kaelthas SAY_MINDCONTROL1'),
	(19622, 10, 1, 'Bow to my will.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11269, 'kaelthas SAY_MINDCONTROL2'),
	(19622, 11, 0, 'Let us see how you fare when your world is turned upside down.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11264, 'kaelthas SAY_GRAVITYLAPSE1'),
	(19622, 11, 1, 'Having trouble staying grounded?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11265, 'kaelthas SAY_GRAVITYLAPSE2'),
	(19622, 12, 0, 'Anara\'nel belore!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11267, 'kaelthas SAY_SUMMON_PHOENIX1'),
	(19622, 12, 1, 'By the power of the sun!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11266, 'kaelthas SAY_SUMMON_PHOENIX2'),
	(19622, 13, 0, 'For...Quel...thalas!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11274, 'kaelthas SAY_DEATH'),
	(20064, 0, 0, 'Prepare yourselves!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11203, 'thaladred SAY_THALADRED_AGGRO'),
	(20064, 1, 0, 'Forgive me, my prince! I have... failed.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11204, 'thaladred SAY_THALADRED_DEATH'),
	(20064, 2, 0, 'sets his gaze on $N!', 16, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'thaladred EMOTE_THALADRED_GAZE'),
	(20060, 0, 0, 'Blood for blood!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11152, 'sanguinar SAY_SANGUINAR_AGGRO'),
	(20060, 1, 0, 'NO! I ...will... not...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11153, 'sanguinar SAY_SANGUINAR_DEATH'),
	(20062, 0, 0, 'The sin\'dore reign supreme!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11117, 'capernian SAY_CAPERNIAN_AGGRO'),
	(20062, 1, 0, 'This is not over!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11118, 'capernian SAY_CAPERNIAN_DEATH'),
	(20063, 0, 0, 'Anar\'alah belore!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11157, 'telonicus SAY_TELONICUS_AGGRO'),
	(20063, 1, 0, 'More perils... await', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11158, 'telonicus SAY_TELONICUS_DEATH'),
	(19516, 0, 0, 'Alert, you are marked for extermination!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11213, 'voidreaver SAY_AGGRO'),
	(19516, 1, 0, 'Extermination, successful.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11215, 'voidreaver SAY_SLAY1'),
	(19516, 1, 1, 'Imbecile life form, no longer functional.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11216, 'voidreaver SAY_SLAY2'),
	(19516, 1, 2, 'Threat neutralized.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11217, 'voidreaver SAY_SLAY3'),
	(19516, 2, 0, 'Systems... shutting... down...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11214, 'voidreaver SAY_DEATH'),
	(19516, 3, 0, 'Alternative measure commencing...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11218, 'voidreaver SAY_POUNDING1'),
	(19516, 3, 1, 'Calculating force parameters...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11219, 'voidreaver SAY_POUNDING2'),
	(19710, 0, 0, 'You have approximately five seconds to live.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11109, 'ironhand SAY_AGGRO_1'),
	(19710, 1, 0, 'With the precise angle and velocity...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11112, 'ironhand SAY_HAMMER_1'),
	(19710, 1, 1, 'Low tech yet quiet effective!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11113, 'ironhand SAY_HAMMER_2'),
	(19710, 2, 0, 'A foregone conclusion.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11110, 'ironhand SAY_SLAY_1'),
	(19710, 2, 1, 'The processing will continue a schedule!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11111, 'ironhand SAY_SLAY_2'),
	(19710, 3, 0, 'My calculations did not...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11114, 'ironhand SAY_DEATH_1'),
	(19710, 4, 0, 'raises his hammer menacingly...', 41, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'ironhand EMOTE_HAMMER'),
	(19221, 0, 0, 'Don\'t value your life very much, do you?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11186, 'sepethrea SAY_AGGRO'),
	(19221, 1, 0, 'I am not alone.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11191, 'sepethrea SAY_SUMMON'),
	(19221, 2, 0, 'Think you can take the heat?', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11189, 'sepethrea SAY_DRAGONS_BREATH_1'),
	(19221, 2, 1, 'Anar\'endal dracon!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11190, 'sepethrea SAY_DRAGONS_BREATH_2'),
	(19221, 3, 0, 'And don\'t come back!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11187, 'sepethrea SAY_SLAY1'),
	(19221, 3, 1, 'En\'dala finel el\'dal', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11188, 'sepethrea SAY_SLAY2'),
	(19221, 4, 0, 'Anu... bala belore...alon.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11192, 'sepethrea SAY_DEATH');
INSERT INTO `creature_text` (`entry`, `groupid`, `id`, `text`, `type`, `language`, `probability`, `emote`, `duration`, `sound`, `comment`) VALUES
	(19220, 0, 0, 'We are on a strict timetable. You will not interfere!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11193, 'pathaleon SAY_AGGRO'),
	(19220, 1, 0, 'I\'m looking for a team player...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11197, 'pathaleon SAY_DOMINATION_1'),
	(19220, 1, 1, 'You work for me now!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'pathaleon SAY_DOMINATION_2'),
	(19220, 2, 0, 'Time to supplement my work force.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11196, 'pathaleon SAY_SUMMON'),
	(19220, 3, 0, 'I prefeer to be hands-on...', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11199, 'pathaleon SAY_ENRAGE'),
	(19220, 4, 0, 'A minor inconvenience.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11194, 'pathaleon SAY_SLAY_1'),
	(19220, 4, 1, 'Looks like you lose.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11195, 'pathaleon SAY_SLAY_2'),
	(19220, 5, 0, 'The project will... continue.', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 11200, 'pathaleon SAY_DEATH'),
	(18262, 0, 0, 'I give up! Please don\'t kill me!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'unkor SAY_SUBMIT'),
	(18588, 0, 0, 'I choose the third option: KILLING YOU!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'floon SAY_FLOON_ATTACK'),
	(18760, 0, 0, 'Ok let\'s get out of here!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'isla starmane SAY_PROGRESS_1'),
	(18760, 1, 0, 'You sure you\'re ready? Take a moment.', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'isla starmane SAY_PROGRESS_2'),
	(18760, 2, 0, 'Alright, let\'s do this!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'isla starmane SAY_PROGRESS_3'),
	(18760, 3, 0, 'Ok, I think I can make it on my own from here. Thank you so much for breaking me out of there!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, 'isla starmane SAY_PROGRESS_4'),
